name: FTX TV Series DAO
description:
Inspired by actual events——FTX grew into the fourth largest crypto exchange in the world. Then, all of a sudden, the $32 billion giant has collapsed, with CEO’s net wealth plummeting 94% in a single day and token price dropping by 85%. What happened?
We explore this, discover this, and find out about cryptocurrencies and FTX.
Proud relationship with http://izumi.finance
